<p>Net income for the nine months ended February 28, 1997 included a charge of approximately $6.6 million for merger costs associated with the acquisition of OnStream Networks, Inc.  Excluding this charge, proforma net income was $291.4 million ($1.57 per share).  Net income for the nine months ended February 29, 1996 included a charge of approximately $69.0 million for merger costs associated with the acquisition of Chipcom Corporation.  Excluding this charge, proforma net income was $197.6 million ($1.12 per share).</p>
<p>Latest third quarter net income compares with consensus analyst estimate of $0.46 per share, according to First Call.</p>
